Lint and compile: run `deno check .\main.ts`

# General Rules

- Use Deno with typescript
- Use Preact for client-side logic
- Use Fresh/Deno for the "site"

# Styling & UI

- Use Tailwind CSS for styling.

# General Code Style & Formatting

- Follow the Airbnb Style Guide for code formatting.
- Use PascalCase for Preact component file names (e.g., UserCard.tsx, not
  user-card.tsx).
- Prefer named exports for components.

# Project Structure & Architecture

- Follow Preact patterns
- All components that have client-side logic must be in islands folder.
- Correctly determine when to use server vs. client components in Preact.
